tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Virtual_Consultation_Data (
  consultation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  patient_id INT,
  doctor_id INT,
  consultation_date DATE,
  consultation_time TIME,
  duration_minutes INT,
  consultation_notes TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE consultation_data ( 
    consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
    doctor_id UUID, 
    patient_id UUID, 
    consultation_date TIMESTAMP, 
    consultation_duration INTERVAL, 
    consultation_type VARCHAR(50) 
);

CREATE TABLE performance_metrics ( 
    metric_id UUID PRIMARY KEY, 
    consultation_id UUID, 
    engagement_score INT, 
    satisfaction_score INT, 
    performance_rating FLOAT, 
    feedback_text TEXT 
);

CREATE TABLE VirtualConsultations (
 consultation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 patient_id INT,
 consultation_date TIMESTAMP,
 consultation_duration INT,
 consultation_outcome TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE PatientMetrics (
 patient_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 total_consultations INT,
 average_consultation_duration FLOAT,
 satisfaction_rating INT,
 last_consultation_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE TrendAnalysis (
 trend_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 trend_name TEXT,
 trend_start_date TIMESTAMP,
 trend_end_date TIMESTAMP,
 trend_analysis_results TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE Virtual_Consultation_Data ( consultation_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
                     patient_id UUID,
                     doctor_id UUID,
                     consultation_date DATE,
                     consultation_duration INT,
                     consultation_rating FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE consultation_requests (
  request_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  consultation_date DATE,
  consultation_time TIME,
  consultation_duration INT,
  consultation_type VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE consultation_feedback (
  feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  request_id INT,
  feedback_date DATE,
  feedback_score INT,
  feedback_comments TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE consultation_metrics (
  metric_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  request_id INT,
  consultation_duration INT,
  consultation_type VARCHAR(255),
  performance_rating INT
);
